Will be executed in this order
if              #If this is true the rest of the block will be skipped, if false it will execute elif
elif            #If this is true the rest of the block will be skipped, if false it will execure else
else            #If this is true full block will have been executed, then execute print statement

Example:
score = 89
if score >= 90:
    print("Grade: A")
elif score >= 80:
    print("Grade: B")
elif score >= 70:
    print("Grade: C")
elif score >= 60:
    print("Grade: D")
else:
    print("Grade: F")


